      "stem": "A monopolist faces this demand and cost schedule: Columns: Q, P, TC.\nQ: 1, P: \\$50, TC: \\$20.\nQ: 2, P: \\$45, TC: \\$30.\nQ: 3, P: \\$40, TC: \\$45.\nQ: 4, P: \\$35, TC: \\$65.\nQ: 5, P: \\$30, TC: \\$95. What is the monopolist's maximum profit (in dollars)? Enter a single integer dollar amount.",
