      "stem": "Devon has Friday evening free. The options are: a six-hour shift at \\$18 per hour, a concert he values at \\$90, or studying for an exam he values at \\$70 in expected better grade. Devon picks the concert. What is the opportunity cost of the concert, in dollars?",
