      "stem": "In the MRU video [*Change in Demand vs. Change in Quantity Demanded*](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9jLlOPqHxLs), the narrator uses a sugary fizzy drink. When the drink's price rises from \\$3 to \\$4, what does the narrator say happens?",
