      "stem": "A small open economy has domestic supply $Q_s = 2P$ and domestic demand $Q_d = 120 - P$ (price in dollars, quantity in units). The world price is \\$20. The government imposes a \\$10 tariff, raising the domestic price to \\$30. How many units are imported after the tariff? Enter a number.",
